I installed from the torrent, used the auto-update feature of Office to install SP1, then installed SP2 manually (since I'd already downloaded it).  The serial that worked for me was W339P-JRCPB-XX8XD-YK49M-7DYCW.  Also, I used this torrent, since there are no seeders on the one you're looking at currently:
